# Changelog

All notable changes to `wenet-profile-manager` will be documented in this file


## Version 0.21.0 (2021-09-06)

 * Add web services to obtain a diversity team.
 * Modify initilaization of the social context builder social relations
   for a created user.
 * Allow to add or update social network relationship.
 * Update common API models references.


## Version 0.20.0 (2021-08-23)

 * Upgrade common version that fix migrate collections stack overflow error.
 * Update the previous community profiles to have the minimum norm to send
  any received incentive to the user.


## Version 0.19.0 (2021-07-01)

 * Migrate to use the module WeNet common library.
 * Change license from MIT to Apache V2.
 * Change norms on the profile to ProtocolNorm.
 * Allow to create an empty community profile.


## Version 0.18.3 (2021-03-31)

 * Upgrade VertX.
 * Add event management to the interaction protocol engine client.


## Version 0.18.2 (2021-03-10)

 * Fix API to allow null for genders.


## Version 0.18.1 (2021-03-09)

 * Fix bug to allow update gender with null.


## Version 0.18.0 (2021-03-08)

 * Add new genders O, non-binary, and not-say.
 * Fix common models.
 * Upgrade Vert.x version.


## Version 0.17.2 (2021-02-15)

 * Fix unit tests problems with new common models.


## Version 0.17.1 (2021-02-01)

 * Change default log file name


## Version 0.17.0 (2021-02-01)

 * Add component key when ask other components.
 * Fix log format
 * Fix openapi to be static


## Version 0.16.0 (2021-01-14)

 * Adapt to the new task models.


## Version 0.15.0 (2020-09-29)

 * Add the web services to manage the community profiles.
 * Add services to obtain the user identifiers.


## Version 0.14.0 (2020-07-17)

 * Split put to put and patch where put modify full profile and patch only the defined parts.


## Version 0.13.0 (2020-06-15)

 * Allow to create a profile with only its identifier.
 * Add the rest of common models defined by Carlo.
 * Implements the trust calculus.


## Version 0.12.1 (2020-04-17)

 * Synchronize common models with task-manager


## Version 0.12.0 (2020-04-17)

 * Define API to manage trust between users.
 * Allow to define a profile with an identifier.
 * Change 'profileId' to 'userId'.


## Version 0.11.0 (2020-03-03)

 * Update API 0.10.0 that change time stamp values from milliseconds to seconds.


## Version 0.10.0 (2020-02-27)

 * Add gitlab CI process
 * Do test using testcontainers to not have to start docker before.


## Version 0.9.0 (2020-02-20)

 * API
   - Replace status to version
   - Delete profile return no content.
 * Migrate to use Vert.x to provide the API implementation


## Version 0.8.0 (2019-10-30)

 * Fix new task models.


## Version 0.7.1 (2019-10-22)

 * Fix python case errors.


## Version 0.7.0 (2019-10-21)

 * Import the team web services.


## Version 0.6.0 (2019-10-18)

 * Migrate from the previous project eu.we_net.interaction_protocol_engine.


## Version 0.5.0 (2019-08-08)

 * Align with other partners.


## Version 0.4.0 (2019-07-26)

 * Add task models and services.
 * Add trust model ad services.
 * Add a better API description.


## Version 0.3.0 (2019-07-15)

 * Add tags to the services.


## Version 0.2.0 (2019-07-01)

 * Add services to manage the communities, the norms , the profiles and the messages.


## Version 0.1.0 (2019-04-08)

 * Project skeleton